body:
@frreiss, Thank you for your reply.

I am debugging this further, and realized that 
[const int rank = inp.dims();](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/v1.2.1/tensorflow/core/kernels/shape_ops.h#L91) returns value `2` as expected. 
May be the output tensor is going wrong somewhere. Needs more debugging here.
